Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:11.42,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}我無法成為女神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:17.25,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}也不會向他人禱告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:22.20,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}別人的話語與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:28.91,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}我清楚真正寶貴之物為何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:36.64,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}我沒有任何多餘的奢望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:42.37,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3\pos(580,60)}我想要的未來就在此處
